n_arrangement: PRELIMINARY NOTES TO AFFIDAVITS: The affidavits in this box presumably relate to the defense of the accused organizations. For classification as to which were exhibits, etc., detailed scrutiny of the affidavits together with related portions of the record will of course be required. The majority of these affidavits are signed originals.
